@model function model_m5_3A(A, M, D)
    # A → D ← M
    σ ~ Exponential(1)
    a ~ Normal(0, 0.2)
    bA ~ Normal(0, 0.5)
    bM ~ Normal(0, 0.5)
    μ = @. a + bA * A + bM * M
    D ~ MvNormal(μ, σ)
    # A → M
    σ_M ~ Exponential(1)
    aM ~ Normal(0, 0.2)
    bAM ~ Normal(0, 0.5)
    μ_M = @. aM + bAM * A
    M ~ MvNormal(μ_M, σ_M)
end

m5_3A = sample(model_m5_3A(d.A, d.M, d.D), NUTS(), 1000)
m5_3A_df = DataFrame(m5_3A)
precis(m5_3A_df)

In [42]:
@model function model_m5_5(N, K)
    a ~ Normal(0, 0.2)
    bN ~ Normal(0, 0.5)
    σ ~ Exponential(1)
    μ = @. a + bN * N
    K ~ MvNormal(μ, σ)
end

m5_5 = sample(model_m5_5(dcc.N, dcc.K), NUTS(), 1000)
m5_5_df = DataFrame(m5_5);
